            <p style="font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; margin: 0;">Lesson 1: Songwriter's Toolbox</p>
            <p style="font-size: 14pt; line-height: 1.2; margin: 5px 0;">
               <i>featuring Singer/Songwriter Shakira</i> <br>Just like a songwriter puts lyrics and notes in the right order to tell a story, programmers put code blocks in a specific sequence to make a program work.
            </p>
        </div>
