             style="width: 10%; border-radius: 10px; margin: 0px 20px 20px 0px;">
        <div>
            <p style="font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; margin: 0;">Lesson 2: Producer Power</p>
            <p style="font-size: 14pt; line-height: 1.2; margin: 5px 0;">
                <i>featuring Producer Henny Tha Bizness</i> <br>A music producer reuses beats, builds patterns, and structures songs efficiently—just like a programmer uses functions to group and reuse code.
            </p>
