        <div>
            <p style="font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; margin: 0;">Lesson 3: Sound Designer’s Studio</p>
            <p style="font-size: 14pt; line-height: 1.2; margin: 5px 0;">
                <i>featuring Artist, Creator, and Coder Roxanne</i> <br> Sound designers make effects that react to what players do in a game—like jumping, colliding, or collecting. In event-driven code runs only when something happens.
